{"tid":121763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家新聞都唔敢再用南亞人呢幾隻字了,海關截非洲毒郵包","createTime":"2017-02-15T13:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T15:53:41.000Z","uid":38740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab60f9067242cf5f2fbc1c97ac760048095e18fc","tid":121763,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"海關截非洲毒郵包<br />\n揭藏140萬大麻拘一男 <br />\n【本報訊】海關人員破獲郵包運毒，前日在元朗八鄉拘捕一名40歲非華裔無業男子，並在包裹內起出5.1公斤懷疑大麻毒品，總值140萬元，行動中，疑人一度反抗企圖逃走，糾纏後被關員制服拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n海關高級調查主任劍雄表示，撿獲的包裹從非洲莫桑比克寄出，以尼龍袋裝運抵港，關員在檢查中發現袋有藏有暗格，上層以海產及草織製品遮掩，下層有6個以鍚紙封裝包裹，包裹內發現懷疑大麻毒品，於是部署行動，將郵包的收貨人拘捕調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170215/19929166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170215%2F19929166&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=87e90e58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170215%2F19929166&h=a83c1f1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170215/19929166</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431dc8748d752be302893440c39fe087112287d0","tid":121763,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"非華裔無業男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係歧視失業<br />\n<br />\n應該叫非華裔非就業男"},{"pid":"45a46aa9a55e7dbb8f7ce7fde6bccc23be7544d9","tid":121763,"uid":7376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非華裔無業男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係歧視失業<br />\n<br />\n應該叫非華裔非就業男</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該叫非華裔非就業非女性先得"},{"pid":"eca184b7e3d79456297a51cf7f5150a92db2224d","tid":121763,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海關截非洲毒郵包<br />\n揭藏140萬大麻拘一男 <br